# Pune Metro Ticketing System 🚇

A simple console-based Pune Metro Ticketing System developed in C++.

This mini project demonstrates the use of:
- Arrays
- Strings
- Loops
- If-Else Statements
- 2D Arrays
- User Input Handling

---

## Features

✅ Display Pune Metro Stations  
✅ Fare Calculation using 2D Array  
✅ Student Discount System  
✅ Ticket Printing  
✅ Multiple Ticket Booking  
✅ Input Validation  

---

## Technologies Used

- C++
- VS Code
- g++

---

## Stations Included

1. PCMC  
2. Sant Tukaram Nagar  
3. Nashik Phata  
4. Shivajinagar  
5. Civil Court  

---

## How to Run

### Compile
```bash
g++ main.cpp -o metro
```

### Run
```bash
./metro
```

